y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外<br />\r\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有個焗到蛋糕/曲奇ge焗爐 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3975de9a32ac206a002a2fbdd3f638bbef5a4b1","tid":906224,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"155e8afd568d626c4b5dd6aa77ef083d6b9e0e2b","tid":906224,"uid":24519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:25:49.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買焗爐<br />\r\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買焗爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n我黎緊想去讀甜品 買個焗爐幾百蚊好似唔太貴<br />\r\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾百蚊食到一個星期了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge二手焗爐讓出黎<br />\r\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n祝各位新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港建國 共匪倒台之外<br />\r\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有個焗到蛋糕/曲奇ge焗爐 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:27:41.000Z","msg":"有冇notebook?<br />\nTG傾"},{"pid":"b117a35f4e5559142617d213f2cc6c5526c7daa8","tid":906224,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb3f9abea2d8ee7581d5aa636b0bc22d286b09d1","tid":906224,"uid":149803,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"女朋友唔見左右，有冇人借條女嚟屌住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T19:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\